name: Jaadu
address: 92 Park Hall Road, West Dulwich SE21 8BW
description: Jaadu is an independent boutique situated in the heart of West Dulwich which opened in May 2013. Jaadu is the Hindi word for magic and the shop is a selection of lovingly curated clothes, soft furnishing, homewares, accessories and jewellery.
